<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<!-- @import "global/head.kit" -->

<body>
    <!-- @import "global/header.kit" -->

    <main class="content">
        <section class="title">
            <h1>Agatha Christie Book Covers</h1>
            <p class="year">2024</p>
        </section>
        <section>
            <p>Agatha Christie's Hercule Poirot series follows the titular detective as he solves murder mysteries around the world. The novels all have a very similar, "cookie cutter" plotline, represented by the basic shapes, and the textures are reminiscent of passport stamps, reflecting Poirot's worldly adventures.</p>
        </section>
        <section class="gallery threeColumn noGap">
            <picture>
                <source
                        media="(min-width: 1440px)"
                        srcset="/assets/bookcover1-xl.png" />
                <source
                        media="(min-width: 1024px)"
                        srcset="/assets/bookcover1-lg.png" />
                <img src="/assets/bookcover1-min.png" alt="Murder on the Orient Express book cover" />
            </picture>
            <picture>
                <source
                        media="(min-width: 1440px)"
                        srcset="/assets/bookcover2-xl.png" />
                <source
                        media="(min-width: 1024px)"
                        srcset="/assets/bookcover2-lg.png" />
                <img src="/assets/bookcover2-min.png" alt="Death on the Nile book cover" />
            </picture>
            <picture>
                <source
                        media="(min-width: 1440px)"
                        srcset="/assets/bookcover3-xl.png" />
                <source
                        media="(min-width: 1024px)"
                        srcset="/assets/bookcover3-lg.png" />
                <img src="/assets/bookcover3-min.png" alt="Evil Under the Sun book cover" />
            </picture>
        </section>
        <section>
            <h2>Process:</h2>
            <img src="/assets/bookcoverprocess.png" alt="" class="maxHeight">
        </section>
        <!-- @import "global/footer.kit" -->

    </main>
</body>
<!-- @import "global/scripts.kit"-->

</html>